”人物》，主演動作劇《瞄準》和科幻懸疑劇《在劫難逃》；2021 年出演電視劇《掃黑風暴》。","name":"張皓然","primary":false}}]}},"person_53936_translations":{"at":1773676877215,"data":{"id":53936,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia\n\nMelonie Díaz (born April 25, 1984) is an American actress who has been appeared in many independent films, including four shown at the 2008 Sundance Film Festival.\n\nDescription above from the Wikipedia article Melonie Díaz , licensed under CC-BY-SA, full list of contributors on Wikipedia.","name":"Melonie Díaz","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"梅洛妮·迪亚兹（Melonie Diaz，1984 年 4 月 25 日出生）是一位美国女演员","name":"梅洛妮·迪亚兹","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Мелоні Діаз","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Мелони Диас","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"梅洛妮·迪亞茲（Melonie Diaz，1984 年 4 月 25 日出生）是一位美國女演員","name":"梅洛妮·迪亞茲","primary":false}}]}},"person_1081493_translations":{"at":1773676881067,"data":{"id":1081493,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Helen Ma Hoi-Lun","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"马海伦，邵氏演员。1960年开始参演多部邵氏电影。1970年加入佳艺电视，演出多套电视剧，如《红楼梦》、《仙鹤神针》、《鹿鼎记》、《神雕侠侣》、《雪山飞狐》等。1978年客串演出丽的电视《天龙诀》。1990年后加入无线电视，曾演出多套电视剧如《天涯歌女》，《